Backers get videos a few days early

31:51.140 --> 31:52.980
and also get to make suggestions

31:52.980 --> 31:54.420
on changes before the other version

31:54.420 --> 31:55.220
goes out,

31:55.220 --> 31:56.980
and they get some bonus extra videos

31:56.980 --> 31:57.700
every now and then.

31:57.700 --> 31:58.660
I still need to finish one

31:58.660 --> 32:00.500
about the making of the control delete video,

32:00.500 --> 32:01.860
but there's just so much footage

32:01.860 --> 32:02.580
to cut together.

32:02.580 --> 32:04.180
I'm basically making a little documentary

32:04.180 --> 32:07.300
about making this silly YouTube video.

32:07.300 --> 32:08.820
Oh, and since I don't do readings

32:08.820 --> 32:10.500
of the credits outside of longer videos,

32:10.500 --> 32:11.540
I'm trying a new thing

32:11.540 --> 32:13.380
where I stream myself to $10 back

32:13.380 --> 32:14.820
as doing editing

32:14.820 --> 32:16.340
and take live suggestions

32:16.340 --> 32:18.820
and show off my sort of process.

32:18.820 --> 32:20.580
Last night, I did a three-hour stream

32:20.580 --> 32:22.820
of me making changes to this video.

32:23.300 --> 32:24.820
So thanks to Mallow,

32:24.820 --> 32:26.420
who was in the chat and gave me the idea

32:26.420 --> 32:28.660
of pointing out that Huelbeck sucks.

32:28.660 --> 32:29.940
I wasn't sure if I should do it,

32:29.940 --> 32:31.060
so it was nice getting the input

32:31.060 --> 32:32.420
that I probably ought to,

32:32.420 --> 32:33.540
and thanks to everyone else

32:33.540 --> 32:34.900
who singled out other changes

32:34.900 --> 32:36.180
and fixes to mistakes

32:36.180 --> 32:39.460
I can now pretend were never made at all.

32:39.460 --> 32:41.860
I'd also like to say a special thank you

32:41.860 --> 32:43.380
to the over 100 people

32:43.380 --> 32:44.180
who reached out to me

32:44.180 --> 32:45.140
when I asked on Twitter

32:45.140 --> 32:46.660
for LGBT fans of Lovecraft

32:46.660 --> 32:48.500
to get in touch a few months ago.

32:48.500 --> 32:49.700
Your notes and contributions

32:49.700 --> 32:50.660
were really great

32:50.660 --> 32:52.100
and helped me think a lot

32:52.100 --> 32:53.060
about this topic

32:53.060 --> 32:55.140
and helped me ascertain

32:55.140 --> 32:57.460
that it wasn't all just me,

32:57.460 --> 32:58.900
that I wasn't imagining all of this,

32:58.900 --> 33:00.340
that other people felt this way.

33:01.140 --> 33:03.380
You were all really helpful and lovely,

33:03.380 --> 33:05.060
and this video wouldn't exist

33:05.060 --> 33:07.380
without your kindness and support.

33:07.380 --> 33:09.300
I hope everyone had a happy Pride Month.

33:09.300 --> 33:11.780
Not that you have to stop being proud now.

33:11.780 --> 33:13.860
You know, by all means, please continue.

33:14.580 --> 33:18.020
I'm going to go back into my hole

33:18.740 --> 33:20.980
and feel sorry for myself

33:20.980 --> 33:22.180
for another 11 months,

33:22.180 --> 33:25.700
but you do whatever makes you feel good.

